+- hint: a short hint if incorrect, or a short reinforcement if correct
+
+Word: ${input.word}
+Correct definition: ${input.correctDefinition}
+Reference example: ${input.exampleSentence || "No reference example provided."}
+Learner definition: ${input.userDefinition}`;
